{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0\u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017400/extras/ember_gif.gif?t=1733261137\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The story goes like this...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Whilst warmth of the stove back home still surrounds your body, you're now awakened on a far-away land. Fairytales of  youth seem to get alive as your sleep deepens more and more. The Dreamrealm has called you, it is in great danger as corruption spreads furthermore. </i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Your task is to make a foothold onto Heidenkalla and find what causes such evil.\u00a0Craft, build and survive the unknown. Make friends or slay foes, do all what it takes to establish peace back in this kingdom of dreams.</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017400/extras/descr2.png?t=1733261137\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use your wits and discover this world of folklore, fairytales and fantasy. While you delve deeper in the matter that has the Dreamrealm threatened there will be all sorts of challanges to best and  even that the isle of Heidenkalla is looking harmless might have you wonder. <br><br>From fighting screaming broodkins to cracking zmei, empowering mushrooms and enchanted apples, either building Castle Ravensthorn or conquering a zmei camp, the choice is yours.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017400/extras/descr2.png?t=1733261137\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017400/extras/gif1-char.gif?t=1733261137\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Select what traits suits your character, but take in consideration that eachone of them will have an output on your gameplay. From a Vitality build to tank monsters, or a Stamina one to deal damage and forage more to a Wisdom build for mainly crafting and building, you'll have to forsee your next move, as isle Heidenkalla might be treacherous if not paying attention. Think twice before you act once, and there might be a chance. <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017400/extras/descr2.png?t=1733261137\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0 \u00a0\u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017400/extras/gif-small1.gif?t=1733261137\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017400/extras/gif-small2.gif?t=1733261137\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Harvest the isle for your own good. Gather foodstuff to manage your stats, materials for building and whatever else you might find useful. Make a campfire and improve your dishes, become best at besting those wilds. Find enchanted goods and discover their power-ups. Use whatever asset you can find to survive this land!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017400/extras/descr2.png?t=1733261137\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0\u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017400/extras/gif1-spider.gif?t=1733261137\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Danger is always close, and death is waiting for you to take a wrong step. Face now your demons and fight off of this land monsters that were long lost. From screaming Broods to fierce Zmei, cleanse the Dreamrealm from evil. You'll never know what else lurks around...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017400/extras/descr2.png?t=1733261137\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0\u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017400/extras/gif2-etc.gif?t=1733261137\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Brace yourself in a new adventure, alone or along friends! Come forth and face the corruption that perils the Dreamrealm. The deep sleep of a warm night must be protected as you fight off intruders in a world long left to rest, and become the next fairytale hero!</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"The Answer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3017400/c52c1519ae5b9ba4c680dd2c2e95db531a851586.jpg"},{"name":"The Dreamer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3017400/c108725ca3598e049701cd7c4df281ad75ccc536.jpg"},{"name":"The Handful","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3017400/8d2fdd8f6c52314f3b5071388d1e35de1aa9f3fd.jpg"},{"name":"Peak Molovach","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3017400/e1613d10253128a3632232a335fcde8c93a23f1e.jpg"},{"name":"The Hoarder","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3017400/b310a29c5cbcc40c78186b9524e304b07c66f797.jpg"},{"name":"The Hungry","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3017400/7b92306ea058163b9f3a64c752c0dfd07ae2c295.jpg"},{"name":"The Sleepy","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3017400/c3716a438c48ef55428df3b059df9228f103da4d.jpg"},{"name":"Stronghold of Faith","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3017400/bb5b9cff7b32727c8e083f02d2c564fef33da180.jpg"},{"name":"Metalworks","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3017400/68e987711870b99f186005cc5c1d632aeea7b116.jpg"},{"name":"Each and any piece.","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamc